cs.MM, cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.IT, cs.IR 

The paper focuses on reversible image watermarking in medical images, which involves image processing and information theory. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.MM (Multimedia), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The use of wavelet transform and distortion compensation also suggests the possibility of cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
